      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kenra Daniels" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kenra Daniels" href="/user/show/5391266-kenra-daniels">Kenra Daniels</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>


          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">anyone who enjoys adult sci-fi, techno thrillers, thrillers</span></div>

        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer869937111" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2359619644350944353">Advances in technology, along with the depths of human depravity and prevalence of corruption makes it likely for human society to be moved into a similar scenario within the next couple of decades. Combined with an exceptionally well-written story and believable characters, those factors make The Meat Market feel just around the corner.<br/><br/>The point of view is intimate and brings the reader right into Jonathon&apos;s heart and mind, and makes the story more important to the reader. There&apos;s a good mix of</span>
  <span id="freeText2359619644350944353" style="display:none">Advances in technology, along with the depths of human depravity and prevalence of corruption makes it likely for human society to be moved into a similar scenario within the next couple of decades. Combined with an exceptionally well-written story and believable characters, those factors make The Meat Market feel just around the corner.<br /><br />The point of view is intimate and brings the reader right into Jonathon's heart and mind, and makes the story more important to the reader. There's a good mix of action and down time that flows naturally, and the dialog and character interactions are well done. The imagery is rich and still trusts the reader's imagination to fill in the details.<br /><br />Overall, this is an excellent read, and I'll definitely buy others in the series. Highly recommended!</span>
  <a data-text-id="2359619644350944353" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

