        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer863460705" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10836494892937856747">Fast paced, this was an easy read while still keeping one’s attention. A tale of lust and greed, it is set in a time far removed from this one. The hero is not a super hero as such. He makes his fair share of mistakes while trying to right a very grave wrong. The particular society he finds himself in is one which is being exploited by those who should be improving the lot of its citizens. The language is gritty the action nonstop. It is a well thought out and well organized story. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


